ers of Quran never enter Hellfire","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 26, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"'Uqbah ibn 'Amir reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIf the Quran were placed in a leatherskin and then thrown into the fire, it would not burn.\u201d Al-Bayhaqi said, \u201cIt means whoever carries the Quran and recites it will never be touched by Hellfire.\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33438,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/09\/12\/umar-convinces-abu-bakr\/","url_meta":{"origin":19379,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Mushaf: Umar convinces Abu Bakr to collect the Quran","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 12, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Zayd ibn Thabit reported: Abu Bak sent for me after the people of Al-Yamamah were killed and Umar ibn al-Khattab was with him. Abu Bakr, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cUmar came to me and said that many reciters of the Quran were killed in the fighting at\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3920,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/07\/31\/quran-advocates-yawm-al-qiyamah\/","url_meta":{"origin":19379,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Quran: Al-Baqarah and Ali &#8216;Imran intercede for reciters","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 31, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Nawwas ibn Sam\u2019an reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cOn the Day of Resurrection, the Quran and its people who acted upon it will be brought forth, preceded by Surat al-Baqarah and Ali 'Imran. It is as if they are two clouds, or two\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17587,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/01\/17\/umar-islam-ruined\/","url_meta":{"origin":19379,"position":3},"title":"Umar on Islam: Muslims ruined by faulty scholars, leaders, hypocrites","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 17, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Ziyad ibn Hudayr reported: Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, said to me, \"Do you know what will dismantle Islam?\" I said no. Umar said, \u201cIslam will be dismantled by the faults of scholars, the bickering of hypocrites over the Book, and the judgments of misguided leaders.\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32421,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/22\/parable-reciters-good-company\/","url_meta":{"origin":19379,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Company: Parable of Quran reciters, righteous friends","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 22, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe parable of the believer who recites the Quran is that of citron, whose fragrance and t